                    <a href="http://www.barrowga.org/uploaded/April30th.pdf">Called Budget Session Meeting</a><br>
                    On  Thursday, April 30 2020 at 4:00p.m. The Barrow County Board of Commissioners will hold a Called Budget Work Session. The meeting will be conducted via Zoom and will be broadcast on the County website http://www.barrowga.org
                </p>
