                    The Barrow County Board of Commissioners Work Session, scheduled for Tuesday April 28, 2020, has been cancelled
                </p>
            </div>
        
            <div class="news_item">
                
                <p>
                    <a href="http://www.barrowga.org/uploaded/NoticeOfPublicMeeting.pdf">Notice Of Public Meeting</a><br>
                    The Barrow County Planning Commission will hold their regularly scheduled meeting on Thursday, April 16. Due to the COVID-19 pandemic the meeting will be broadcast, live, via Facebook Live. Please click on link above for details.
                </p>
            </div>
        
            <div class="news_item">
                
                <p>
                    <a href="http://www.barrowga.org/uploaded/OrdertoEnsureHealthyGA.pdf">The Governor of The State of Georgia Executive Order Regarding COVID-19</a><br>
                    On April 2nd Governor Kemp signed an Executive Order that contains, among other things, a statewide shelter-in-place provision.  This Executive Order, which takes effect at 6:00 PM on April 3rd, supersedes and makes void any conflicting local government emergency order currently in place.  Please click here for a full copy of the Governor’s Executive Order.

For additional information, please <a href="http://www.barrowga.org/uploaded/StatewideShelterGov.pdf">click here</a> for a summary of the Executive Order prepared by the Association of County Commissioners of Georgia and the Georgia Municipal Association.
                </p>
            </div>
        
